Eugenie Bouchard refused to shake the hand of Alexandra Dulgheru before a Fed Cup match at the weekend . 
  The Canadian lost both her singles matches to the Romanian ranked 69 and 104 . 
  The 21-year-old reached the Wimbledon final last year but has struggled this year . 
  She has often been compared to Maria Sharapova and has been mocked for refusing to shake hands before matches . 
 